Task 2: Extract GPS Metadata Using ExifTool
Step 2.1: View All Metadata
Extract complete metadata from a single image:

# Navigate to sample images
cd ~/gps_lab/sample_images

# View all EXIF data (replace IMAGE.jpg with your filename)
exiftool IMAGE.jpg

# View only GPS-related tags
exiftool -GPS* IMAGE.jpg
