Troubleshooting Tips
No GPS data found in images:

Verify location services were enabled when photos were taken
Check if images were edited/processed (may strip metadata)
Use exiftool -a -G1 IMAGE.jpg to view all metadata groups
Python import errors:

Ensure pip3 packages installed: pip3 install --user pillow exifread folium
Check Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.6+)
Use virtual environment if system packages conflict
Coordinate conversion issues:

Verify DMS format in EXIF data matches expected structure
Check reference values (N/S/E/W) are present
Handle missing or malformed GPS tags gracefully
Map not displaying correctly:

Ensure output HTML file has proper permissions
Check browser console for JavaScript errors
Verify folium library version: pip3 show folium
